{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"You know, what I do is write for children,"},{"time":3000,"text":"and I'm probably America's"},{"time":5000,"text":"most widely read children's author, in fact."},{"time":7000,"text":"And I always tell people"},{"time":9000,"text":"that I don't want to show up looking like a scientist."},{"time":12000,"text":"You can have me as a farmer, or in leathers,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and no one has ever chose farmer."},{"time":19000,"text":"I'm here today to talk to you"},{"time":21000,"text":"about circles and epiphanies."},{"time":23000,"text":"And you know, an epiphany"},{"time":25000,"text":"is usually something you find that you dropped someplace."},{"time":27000,"text":"You've just got to go around the block"},{"time":29000,"text":"to see it as an epiphany."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"That's a painting of a circle."},{"time":33000,"text":"A friend of mine did that -- Richard Bollingbroke."},{"time":36000,"text":"It's the kind of complicated circle"},{"time":38000,"text":"that I'm going to tell you about."},{"time":40000,"text":"My circle began back in the '60s"},{"time":43000,"text":"in high school in Stow, Ohio"},{"time":45000,"text":"where I was the class queer."},{"time":48000,"text":"I was the guy beaten up bloody"},{"time":50000,"text":"every week in the boys' room,"},{"time":52000,"text":"until one teacher saved my life."},{"time":55000,"text":"She saved my life by letting me go to the bathroom"},{"time":58000,"text":"in the teachers' lounge."},{"time":60000,"text":"She did it in secret."},{"time":62000,"text":"She did it for three years."},{"time":64000,"text":"And I had to get out of town."},{"time":67000,"text":"I had a thumb, I had 85 dollars,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and I ended up in San Francisco, California --"},{"time":73000,"text":"met a lover --"},{"time":76000,"text":"and back in the '80s, found it necessary"},{"time":78000,"text":"to begin work on AIDS organizations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83000,"text":"About three or four years ago,"},{"time":85000,"text":"I got a phone call in the middle of the night"},{"time":87000,"text":"from that teacher, Mrs. Posten,"},{"time":90000,"text":"who said, \"I need to see you."},{"time":92000,"text":"I'm disappointed"},{"time":94000,"text":"that we never got to know each other as adults."},{"time":97000,"text":"Could you please come to Ohio,"},{"time":100000,"text":"and please bring that man"},{"time":102000,"text":"that I know you have found by now."},{"time":105000,"text":"And I should mention"},{"time":107000,"text":"that I have pancreatic cancer,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and I'd like you to please"},{"time":112000,"text":"be quick about this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"Well, the next day we were in Cleveland."},{"time":117000,"text":"We took a look at her, we laughed, we cried,"},{"time":120000,"text":"and we knew that she needed to be in a hospice."},{"time":124000,"text":"We found her one, we got her there,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and we took care of her"},{"time":128000,"text":"and watched over her family,"},{"time":130000,"text":"because it was necessary."},{"time":132000,"text":"It's something we knew how to do."},{"time":134000,"text":"And just as the woman who wanted to know me as an adult"},{"time":138000,"text":"got to know me,"},{"time":140000,"text":"she turned into a box of ashes"},{"time":142000,"text":"and was placed in my hands."},{"time":145000,"text":"And what had happened"},{"time":147000,"text":"was the circle had closed,"},{"time":149000,"text":"it had become a circle --"},{"time":152000,"text":"and that epiphany I talked about"},{"time":154000,"text":"presented itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156000,"text":"The epiphany is"},{"time":158000,"text":"that death is a part of life."},{"time":160000,"text":"She saved my life;"},{"time":163000,"text":"I and my partner saved hers."},{"time":167000,"text":"And you know, that part of life needs everything"},{"time":169000,"text":"that the rest of life does."},{"time":171000,"text":"It needs truth and beauty,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and I'm so happy it's been mentioned so much here today."},{"time":176000,"text":"It also needs --"},{"time":179000,"text":"it needs dignity,"},{"time":181000,"text":"love and pleasure,"},{"time":183000,"text":"and it's our job to hand those things out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}